OL,8,Fthree-year-old son has admitted
OL,9,Fhitting him with a bamboo cane but
OL,10,Fsays she was allowed to because the
OL,11,FBible told her she "should chastise
OL,12,Fher child", a court heard.
OL,14,FChristina Robinson at their home in
OL,15,FUshaw Moor, in County Durham, in
OL,16,FNovember 2022.
OL,18,FThe 30-year-old is standing trial at ,
OL,19,Fwhere she also denies a child cruelty
