OL,7,FHe was taken to hospital but died
OL,8,Fshortly after.
OL,10,FFollowing his death, medical experts
OL,11,Fsaid there were signs he had been the
OL,12,Fvictim of a series of assaults and had
OL,13,Fsustained a number of non-accidental
OL,14,Finjuries.
OL,16,FThere was also evidence Dwelaniyah had
OL,17,Fbeen beaten with a bamboo cane, the
OL,18,Fcourt heard.
