OL,7,FRichard Wright KC, prosecuting, said:
OL,8,F"The defendant admits that she hit him
OL,9,Fwith a weapon but says that she was
OL,10,Fallowed to do so because the bible
OL,11,Ftells her that she should chastise her
OL,12,Fchild."
OL,14,FAt the time of his death, Dwelaniyah's
OL,15,Flegs were heavily bandaged due to
OL,16,Fburns, which the court heard had
OL,17,Fcovered about 15-20% of his body.
OL,19,FRobinson said they had been caused
OL,20,Fwhen he was messing about in the
OL,21,Fshower a few weeks earlier.
