OL,7,FMr Wright said evidence suggests they
OL,8,Fhad been caused by Dwelaniyah sitting
OL,9,Fin scalding hot water.
OL,11,FHe told the court he had suffered a
OL,12,F"major head injury" before his
OL,13,Fcollapse, of the type that could have
OL,14,Fbeen caused by forceful shaking,
OL,15,Flikely striking his head off a surface
OL,16,For object.
OL,18,FHis death was not caused by choking on
OL,19,Fa cheese bun, Mr Wright added.
