OL,7,FHe said: "The prosecution say the
OL,8,Fdeath of Dwelaniyah was not an
OL,9,Faccident but the end point in a series
OL,10,Fof violent and cruel acts perpetrated
OL,11,Fagainst him by his mother Christina
OL,12,FRobinson.
OL,14,F"She injured him, she neglected to
OL,15,Ftreat the injuries that she inflicted
OL,16,Fupon her and then she murdered him."
OL,18,FShe denies murder and child cruelty.
OL,20,FThe trial continues.
